{
  "stem": "24830.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were talking about how-- how things had changed so much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you-- you mentioned that that an Aryan administrator was put in charge of your parents'--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, instead of my-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I see her every day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, she came every day to the business.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was her job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But can I finish the law?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because after all these law were, I told you, very slow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the two-- the two worse one were, you cannot go-- you cannot go out from the [INAUDIBLE]-- you cannot go out between the-- between 8 o'clock in the-- 8 o'clock in the morning-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] no. 6 o'clock in the morning-- you can go out between 6 o'clock in the morning till 8 o'clock at night, in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You couldn't go out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then, you couldn't go to the-- you couldn't go to the theater.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You couldn't use a phone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You couldn't go to the restaurant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You couldn't go to the library.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You couldn't go to park.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the people who has a job, like teacher, or for the government-- they couldn't-- they couldn't work anymore.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And if you were a French officer [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in the French-- in the French army, you didn't belong to the French army anymore.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the French considered them-- you know, they have been born there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because before, they started by attacking all the foreigner or people-- but then they started with the French.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then the last-- the last law, which is the worst one, they thought, well, it's-- the Jew are not visible enough.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's not always written in your face.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So they decided that you have to have a Jewish star, which is the Magen David.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
